The past is gone
The real fad for personal money management only hit <COREF ID="44" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> in the mid-1980s .
It was then that <COREF ID="44" TYPE="IDENT">the country 's</COREF> accumulated economic resources began to come to the surface .
