" <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">Investors</COREF> sometimes act as if <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> do n't care about a company 's current losses , but simply put all <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">their</COREF> faith in the distant future .
