The misguided idea that " what is new is better " also has been a problem in Taiwan .
<COREF ID="70" TYPE="IDENT">A certain " Mr. Wang , " who works in the government</COREF> , <COREF ID="68" TYPE="IDENT">last year</COREF> thought <COREF ID="70" TYPE="IDENT">he</COREF> would jump on the bandwagon for telecom and Internet stocks .
