Cabula Chang , editor - in - chief of the money management website SmartNet , describes a case in point .
<COREF ID="68" TYPE="IDENT">Last year</COREF> , <COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT">one of the hottest stocks</COREF> was Quanta Computers , which reached 800 per share .
